com.truecaller.assignment.application.model.manager

Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.truecaller.assignment.application.model.manager.Manager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SerializeAndDeserializePOJORules, WebServiceRules
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccountManager

    public abstract class Manager
extends java.lang.Object
implements WebServiceRules, SerializeAndDeserializePOJORules
    This main manager class. Every module manager must extend this class, to use its common functionality. Like make webservice call using GET POST. and return data from API in AddData dataType. you can also write pojo OR Bean objects to internal file system using Serialization technique of JAVA. Created by Hukum on 12/5/15.
